-- Towers of Hanoi (7 disks) -- durability proof, not computation.
-- Pre-computed 127 moves. Agent just closes steps. Proves crash-recovery at scale.

## towers-of-hanoi-7

  input param.source_peg : str default("A")
  input param.target_peg : str default("C")
  input param.auxiliary_peg : str default("B")

  # setup : text
    user>
      Verify initial state: all 7 disks stacked on peg {{param.source_peg}}.
      Largest on bottom.
    accept>
      Initial state verified.
  #/

